31:53.423 --> 31:56.392
Mrs. Johnson, carly's told me
how kind you've been to her.

31:56.460 --> 31:58.861
Oh, we've been having
so much fun at rehearsals,
haven't we?

31:58.928 --> 32:00.963
<i>I'd like you
to meet my son glenn.</i>

32:01.030 --> 32:03.666
This is mrs. Marshall.
Mrs. Marshall,
how do you do?

32:03.767 --> 32:06.902
Rebecca and alexandra.

32:07.271 --> 32:10.573
You're going to west point
in the fall?
Yes, ma'am, if they'll have me.

32:10.774 --> 32:14.310
They haven't turned down
a johnson in five generations.
They'll be lucky to get you.

32:14.378 --> 32:18.547
I've always said that
vince was born to command
and I was born to demand.

32:18.782 --> 32:22.785
it's lucky you two
found each other.

32:22.786 --> 32:25.655
Would you two like
to play some croquet?
Go on.

32:25.722 --> 32:27.990
Go on, go play.
Okay.

32:28.057 --> 32:31.026
<i>You've got a real bevy
of beauties here, major.
I envy you.</i>

32:31.295 --> 32:34.797
