who can't make friends.

33:16.039 --> 33:18.974
We've been here two months
and neither one of you
has brought home a friend.

33:19.042 --> 33:21.644
Dad, most of your colleagues
around here...

33:21.845 --> 33:26.014
Are dedicated to a program
of armed nuclear destruction.

33:26.350 --> 33:30.686
<i>I think they're cretins
and that makes their
offspring sub-cretins.</i>

33:30.754 --> 33:33.489
If you have a problem
with sub-cretins, don't sit
at home and complain about it.

33:33.557 --> 33:36.459
Go forth and enlighten them.

33:36.827 --> 33:41.831
Yeah, maybe I'll start the first
teens for test ban club.

33:41.865 --> 33:44.265
<i>That should make me
real popular around here.</i>

33:44.333 --> 33:46.435
Run away from home
and change your name first.

33:47.937 --> 33:50.939
I really
appreciate this, carly.

33:51.006 --> 33:53.775
Oh, I like to do it.

33:53.843 --> 33:57.278
