so stylish.

33:57.346 --> 34:02.050
Women like you
are the reason that men
like women in the first place.

34:02.117 --> 34:04.052
well.

34:04.119 --> 34:08.121
A woman's charm
is mostly illusion
after all.

34:11.126 --> 34:16.063
I suppose we all have
to grow old some day.

34:16.466 --> 34:20.134
I just don't think
you gotta look bad
in the process.

34:24.139 --> 34:28.577
I see these fine
little lines in my face.

34:28.643 --> 34:31.580
They're called wrinkles, honey.
You might as well
get used to it now.

34:31.647 --> 34:36.083
I look in the mirror sometimes
and I see this old woman
lurking there...

34:36.150 --> 34:38.587
Just waiting to grab me.

34:38.654 --> 34:41.790
Oh, I just get so frightened.

34:41.991 --> 34:44.257
Carly, you have
such an active imagination.

34:44.326 --> 34:46.427
I've seen you
in those rehearsals.

34:46.496 --> 34:50.599
Come on, don't you think that
good posture and keeping fit
and keeping active...

34:50.666 --> 34:53.301
Is all a part
of keeping young too?

34:53.503 --> 34:56.004
Maybe if you're a woodpecker.

34:59.341 --> 35:04.513
Welcome to the fort matthews
hail and farewell dance.

35:16.626 --> 35:18.560
Come on and dance with me.
No.

35:18.628 --> 35:20.729
Yes. Yes, you can.
I can't dance.

35:20.796 --> 35:23.197
<i>Major, I'm glad
you could make it.
Yes, sir.</i>

35:23.265 --> 35:25.533
This is ray stevens
from the atomic
energy commission.

35:25.535 --> 35:30.238
I have heard that gentlemen
from the a.E.C. Are much better
dancers than military men.

35:30.305 --> 35:33.975
Is that true?
My husband won't
dance with me.

35:34.043 --> 35:38.246
The only time I really
enjoyed dancing was when
I was in the service.

35:38.313 --> 35:40.248
<i>That was years ago.
Hmm.</i>

35:40.315 --> 35:45.754
It's left up to me to uphold
the honor of the military
on the dance floor.

35:45.821 --> 35:47.556
<i>Shall we?</i>

35:50.159 --> 35:53.261
You two just share some
atomic secrets or something.

35:53.563 --> 35:55.997
I don't know
if I can take this.

35:56.065 --> 35:59.000
Oh, yeah, you can.

35:59.068 --> 36:01.102
You like it.

36:05.575 --> 36:08.543
I didn't risk my ass in guam
so some damn harvard boy...

36:08.611 --> 36:10.545
Could run this country
into the toilet.

36:10.613 --> 36:14.049
If he can't stand up
to the damn communists,
let us do our jobs.

36:14.116 --> 36:18.286
To hell with nevada,
we'll use havana
for a test site.

36:26.596 --> 36:29.230
I know you're
a strong supporter
of underground testing.

36:29.298 --> 36:33.518
