You don't even care about me.

48:47.316 --> 48:49.251
You just want to know
about all the sex stuff!

48:49.318 --> 48:52.421
Don't you sass me, sister!
I am not your sister!

48:52.489 --> 48:56.825
Well, if I had a sister,
I would tell her everything!

49:03.266 --> 49:07.369
Especially... About boys.

49:07.437 --> 49:09.438
Ew, boys.

49:29.426 --> 49:31.059
What are you-
what are you doing here?

49:31.127 --> 49:34.530
I've come to kidnap you
and take you to the woods.
I left my knife at the bungalow.

49:34.931 --> 49:37.733
<i>Will you come with?
Glenn, that place
is dangerous.</i>

49:37.801 --> 49:41.236
<i>- Not anymore.
My dad had it cleaned up.
- If my mom finds out-</i>

49:41.304 --> 49:44.239
She's gonna be at rehearsal
for hours. Come on.

49:44.307 --> 49:47.075
I've gotta finish up
my chores.

49:47.143 --> 49:49.745
